graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>v1.21.0-18]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js >= 18.0.0]
    Dashboard -->|web framework| Fastify[Fastify ^4.16.0]
    Dashboard -->|UI framework| React[React ^18.x]
    Dashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly ^5.3.x]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient[kubernetes/client-node ^0.12.2]
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy]

    %% External Infrastructure
    Dashboard -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    Dashboard -->|OAuth flow| OSAuth[OpenShift OAuth]

    %% Optional External Dependencies
    Dashboard -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Dashboard -.->|console link| OSConsole[OpenShift Console 4.x]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - CRD Management
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>kubeflow.org/notebooks]
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| KServe[KServe<br/>serving.kserve.io]
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| ModelMesh[Model Mesh<br/>CRD]
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| DSCluster[Data Science Cluster Operator<br/>datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io]
    Dashboard -->|manages CRDs| MROperator[Model Registry Operator<br/>modelregistry.opendatahub.io]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - HTTP Proxy
    Dashboard -->|HTTP proxy| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines]
    Dashboard -->|HTTP proxy| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    Dashboard -->|HTTP proxy| MLMD[ML Metadata MLMD]
    Dashboard -->|HTTP proxy| TrustyAI[TrustyAI]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - API Integration
    Dashboard -->|API calls| Builds[OpenShift Builds<br/>build.openshift.io]
    Dashboard -->|API calls| ImageStreams[OpenShift ImageStreams<br/>image.openshift.io]
    Dashboard -.->|API calls| RHOAM[Red Hat Integration RHOAM<br/>integreatly.org/rhmis]

    %% Integration Points
    OSConsole -->|ConsoleLink| Dashboard

